# ===== SECURITY: Ignore all sensitive files =====
# Passwords and credentials
password.txt
**/password.txt
*.key
*.pem
*.crt

# Environment files with secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# ===== DOCUMENTATION: Only allow README.md files =====
# Ignore ALL .md files
*.md
# Then explicitly allow README.md files anywhere
!README.md
!**/README.md

# Ignore ALL .txt files except requirements
*.txt
# Allow requirements files
!requirements.txt
!requirements-*.txt
!**/requirements.txt
!**/requirements-*.txt

# Ignore security and deployment documentation
SECURITY_*.md
SECURITY_*.txt
**/RAILWAY_DEPLOYMENT.md
**/BACKEND_SETUP.md
**/README_RAILWAY.md

# ===== BUILD & DEPENDENCIES =====
/build/
/dist/
/node_modules/

# Ignore IDE specific files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace
